{"tid":715752,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊8月尾由大阪去東京想坐夜巴","createTime":"2018-06-24T17:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T08:29:27.000Z","uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ce147b0d296da059f187e557d721e367f25977","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"各位有坐過嘅巴絲, 有冇推薦話坐邊間會舒服啲/你地覺得值得坐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好叫小弟坐新幹線/內陸機, 小弟住宿嗰邊book好咗遷就唔到個時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以的話分享吓成個流程可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3c1f5915ac8632c6837eea33f4cdf6e3aabbac","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71d066835593df9813f077b802c4b64ebce3e0b0","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85add6bd52d8594a503fc3d6edcd9f96bb4ed8a6","tid":715752,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"backpacker. com"},{"pid":"416db0239ea4f76185255ad0410931d7c2caa4f6","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8f6cfb6fb177bacb6f2c7ad567722319b1c94e9","tid":715752,"uid":153878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"willer express/JR巴士"},{"pid":"fe18686cdfd5b5d7cc9989110ae39aec19941ec2","tid":715752,"uid":123919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"應該俾得外國人訂得幾個<br />\n啱啱search咗有<br />\n<a href=\"http://willerexpress.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwillerexpress.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d34a3fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://willerexpress.com/tw/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kosokubus.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e5532f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/</a><br />\n好似都俾你用credit card訂 (利伸冇用過)<br />\n其他應要日本國內係7-11個俾錢先得<br />\nD位你最好BOOK獨立咁成晚唔使同個陌生人一齊 <br />\n因為你要瞓個D<br />\n(你想同日本妹一齊另計 不過小心俾人屈你做痴漢)<br />\n同埋見到闊D最好BOOK闊D 太窄你會好辛苦<br />\n係京都見過架來往大阪東京嘅有兩層好豪華 不過唔知邊度有喇"},{"pid":"9a9badfb818b5f0375d70193d7e09793f026442e","tid":715752,"uid":81333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"試過willer express <br />\n少人搭可以訓落啲就舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你預左都幾焗同埋腳伸唔哂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過一晚半晚都可以接受既 慳錢慳時間"},{"pid":"df39b67c376690969ae656d54ba4c4593b4b1382","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe18686cdfd5b5d7cc9989110ae39aec19941ec2","tid":715752,"uid":123919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"應該俾得外國人訂得幾個<br />\n啱啱search咗有<br />\n<a href=\"http://willerexpress.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwillerexpress.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d34a3fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://willerexpress.com/tw/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kosokubus.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e5532f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/</a><br />\n好似都俾你用credit card訂 (利伸冇用過)<br />\n其他應要日本國內係7-11個俾錢先得<br />\nD位你最好BOOK獨立咁成晚唔使同個陌生人一齊 <br />\n因為你要瞓個D<br />\n(你想同日本妹一齊另計 不過小心俾人屈你做痴漢)<br />\n同埋見到闊D最好BOOK闊D 太窄你會好辛苦<br />\n係京都見過架來往大阪東京嘅有兩層好豪華 不過唔知邊度有喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊間巴士公司比較好?"},{"pid":"b501d06b326a61ca25a7be7a39b1f50eb0cdceaf","tid":715752,"uid":123919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df39b67c376690969ae656d54ba4c4593b4b1382","tid":715752,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe18686cdfd5b5d7cc9989110ae39aec19941ec2","tid":715752,"uid":123919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"應該俾得外國人訂得幾個<br />\n啱啱search咗有<br />\n<a href=\"http://willerexpress.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwillerexpress.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d34a3fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://willerexpress.com/tw/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kosokubus.com%2Ftw%2F&d=RE2hEpBSlCMTmGe7FgdyfDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e5532f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kosokubus.com/tw/</a><br />\n好似都俾你用credit card訂 (利伸冇用過)<br />\n其他應要日本國內係7-11個俾錢先得<br />\nD位你最好BOOK獨立咁成晚唔使同個陌生人一齊 <br />\n因為你要瞓個D<br />\n(你想同日本妹一齊另計 不過小心俾人屈你做痴漢)<br />\n同埋見到闊D最好BOOK闊D 太窄你會好辛苦<br />\n係京都見過架來往大阪東京嘅有兩層好豪華 不過唔知邊度有喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊間巴士公司比較好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我兩間都冇搭過其實<br />\n我之前係日本是但禁個D公司都幾好<br />\n我諗呢兩間都差唔多掛 係日本又好少見到D污髒嘅<br />\n唔知你幾高啦 你揀個平D同望落舒服D大D仲好"},{"pid":"beb18ec476d842dd53ed105d544c04860f9c1459","tid":715752,"uid":126165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"你係想慳錢定想體驗下<br />\n如果係慳錢嘅話搭飛機仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f66b4d9365a81d6631b7cab8447f2ae2e9b72d1","tid":715752,"uid":12597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"我上次坐willer（不過係東京去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n坐呢隻車款<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/015750_9c23e7a10467aac3feeba80a6c6e42a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F015750_9c23e7a10467aac3feeba80a6c6e42a2.png&h=27e58888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲位都幾大，鬆動過飛機經濟倉<br />\n有得叉電但記得拎埋插蘇上車<br />\n同埋隔一個鐘會停一停比你去痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預有啲人唔訓用電話會'殘'到你 不過一晚半晚都ok嘅 又慳一晚酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a26693d4e9d67ccd9e6a1c1befd3c62b5c203e","tid":715752,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"坐過willerexpress同另外一間唔記得乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由東京去名古屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6個鐘左右夜晚坐到第二朝清晨<br />\n我自己就揀單丁位 之後都覺後選擇正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個位對走廊嗰面有得拉簾 單丁位另一邊即係窗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以私隱度都幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n優點<br />\n首先d位算舒服 但如果你想挨後張凳 要同後面嗰個單聲<br />\n大gip放車底 其他可以拎上個位 有張被仔 有酒店拖鞋 有衣架 有腳踏 有usb叉電(不過冇電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n開車就會熄燈好似戲院咁黑 慢慢你就會訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中途會停2 3個點比你痾尿<br />\n<br />\n平，慳返晚酒店錢  <br />\n<br />\n缺點<br />\n因為每次停車痾尿，會開燈+廣播(細細聲)，但點都會吵醒 講緊係 2點 4點 咁 所以成晚好難訓得惗<br />\n<br />\n其次，高速公路都ok，有d路震過貓王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又會醒一醒<br />\n<br />\n然後 一落車成身散散地 又立痴痴 除非即刻去酒店 如果唔係冇地方比你梳洗"},{"pid":"211491aba19bcd6105824c487adcf93619f3a69e","tid":715752,"uid":123919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐過willerexpress同另外一間唔記得乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由東京去名古屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6個鐘左右夜晚坐到第二朝清晨<br />\n我自己就揀單丁位 之後都覺後選擇正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個位對走廊嗰面有得拉簾 單丁位另一邊即係窗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以私隱度都幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n優點<br />\n首先d位算舒服 但如果你想挨後張凳 要同後面嗰個單聲<br />\n大gip放車底 其他可以拎上個位 有張被仔 有酒店拖鞋 有衣架 有腳踏 有usb叉電(不過冇電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n開車就會熄燈好似戲院咁黑 慢慢你就會訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中途會停2 3個點比你痾尿<br />\n<br />\n平，慳返晚酒店錢  <br />\n<br />\n缺點<br />\n因為每次停車痾尿，會開燈+廣播(細細聲)，但點都會吵醒 講緊係 2點 4點 咁 所以成晚好難訓得惗<br />\n<br />\n其次，高速公路都ok，有d路震過貓王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又會醒一醒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然後 一落車成身散散地 又立痴痴 除非即刻去酒店 如果唔係冇地方比你梳洗</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搭過名古屋去廣島 8個鐘好似<br />\n到個時我淨係想去瞓<br />\n係車到唔係好瞓得到我覺得 兩三個鍾會醒一次<br />\n同埋去到尾會明明好攰但係瞓唔著<br />\n邊間都好 d櫈都會坐到屎忽發熱嘅<br />\n不過我見有d人可以瞓到扯鼻鼾 應該睇都人嘅<br />\n仲有睇返好少少d位唔係好平<br />\n如果想體驗吓嘅冇所謂 但係如果有d錢搭新幹線啦<br />\n<br />\n不過香港真係冇夜行巴士 樓主後生嘅話可以試吓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4c66e0b3864c1bf2bff63cf24eb29039235b11","tid":715752,"uid":17047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"上星期坐過willerexpress 不過係東京去京都<br />\n係3人一排<br />\n不過最麻煩都係瞓得唔好同埋冇得沖涼痴淋淋"},{"pid":"31aac9efc61f14cb8f3abee8d5d08e6254772e33","tid":715752,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c79016534121179ce35d468de19770323b7730a0","tid":715752,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"唔好貪平坐4列<br />\n辛苦到PK<br />\n<br />\n比多少少坐3列當酒店錢好過<br />\n起碼有覺訓第2日有精神活動<br />\n<br />\n除非你克苦耐勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb42112cc58aad0b090c4f0fd63667651e7fda20","tid":715752,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"試過由大阪坐過夜巴士去名古屋 好似叫jamjam 如果你係唔焗得嗰種人就最好唔好坐 我女友就係人辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢焗到成程係咁咳 完全訓唔到仲要流鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗番起都好 &quot;呢hea&quot;"}]}